# XenonRecomp Altivec/VMX instruction patches
#
# TODO: Copy patches from the vig8 project if the same instruction support
# is needed, or generate new patches specific to The Simpsons Arcade binary.
#
# The vig8 project required adding 30+ missing Altivec/VMX instruction handlers
# to XenonRecomp. The Simpsons Arcade may require the same or different patches
# depending on what instructions its code uses.
#
# Key instruction categories that may need patching:
# - Vector saturating arithmetic (vaddsbs, vaddsws, vsubsbs, vsubshs)
# - Vector shifts (vslh, vsrh, vsrah, vsrab, vrlh)
# - Vector compare (vcmpequh, vcmpgtsh, vcmpgtsw with RC bit)
# - Vector pack (vpkshss, vpkswss, vpkswus, vpkuhus + 128-bit variants)
# - Vector misc (vmaxsh, vminsh, vavguh, vspltish, vslo, vnor)
# - Float conversion (vcfpuxws128)
# - CR bit ops (cror, crorc)
